Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you asking about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You aren't thinking about joining them, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:16.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:19.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And besides! Why the heck is my head on another body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:21.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or maybe it's a fresh corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:22.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So fun! So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:28.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think will happen to us if the cops see that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:30.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care if it's dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:32.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have no other choice, destroy it on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like I won't be able to afford any luxuries this month.{i didn't time the ugh on purpose}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next, I need a kitchen sponge and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:07.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the black bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.18,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It must be around the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:33.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoa! It's the black bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gotta take a pic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is unreal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:38.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? So you bumped into this beauty on the street,{3.36.04 start if you don't want the hohum at the start}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}who was being chased by this evil girl on a bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}has amnesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and had fallen asleep from fatigue by the time I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:47.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you asking me to believe a story I'd only have in my wildest dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, I'm serious! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:54.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, if this had happened in the morning and made you late for school, it'd be stereotypical. {try keeping that archetype and stereotype in next line for the pun explained later OR (preferably) find something better}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and if she'd been a transfer student, it'd be archetypical!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:02.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And if she'd been the princess of a kingdom, and in truth, your childhood friend, it'd be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you get my "stereotypical" and "archetypical" pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, you ruined it by explaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know what to do. She lost her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but she doesn't want to go to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... Well, let's wait and see how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For now, let's wait till tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we'll decide what to do after hearing her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, catch you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.95,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The girl on the black bike might remember my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.17,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That black bike, considered to be an urban legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:47.01,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What can I do against her now that she's my enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hated my easygoing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.77,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted a different life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe that's why I brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.03,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But there's something Kida-kun doesn't know about:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.26,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}her scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:14.49,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's as if someone decapitated her and then forcefully sewed her head back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is an announcement from the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:21.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The jumbo melon breads have sold out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Sup, Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened to that sleeping beauty in your run-down apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keep it down, Kida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? A beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.76,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That word doesn't go unnoticed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When Mikado rounded the corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he bumped into a babe who was being chased by a baddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And now, he's living together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:44.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh... It's just Mr. A/C's fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Ryuugamine, not "Mr. A/C."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyone want to buy me meal tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no need to worry. No one will believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, how's the chick doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She was still sleeping when I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Guess she's really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:10.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The reason why I ate lunch early, in fourth period, is because I'm trying to use my lunch break effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dollars Probability Predictions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is all the rage in our class right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The whole Dollars story is veiled in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So at school, we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Doesn't that guy look like one of the Dollars?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and vote on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like you guys have a lot of votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, each person can vote for several people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:38.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This Takiguchi guy from Class 1-D only has one vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:44.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I, Lord Kida Masaomi, hath given him that vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:47.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm actually in the same P.E. class as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:51.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm strongly convinced that Takiguchi Ryou is a member of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, I'm gonna go check him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Scuze me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is Takiguchi Ryou-kun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is he in the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dunno. Maybe the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think he usually goes up there during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe he's having a smoke break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shouldn't we... not do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There might be scary people up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just kidding, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Smoking on the rooftop during lunch is only in those ancient, clichéd comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if you just ask him if he's a member of the Dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I doubt he'll honestly say, "Yes, I am."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dude, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-He's smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Takiguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you compose songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you a member of the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:04.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was absolutely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:11.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got great instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're that famous guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me? Famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:27.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh, Takiguchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you join the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hm... Now that you ask me out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it was six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Some stranger invited me via a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:56.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He said that they didn't have any rules or restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At first I was like, "No way,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but then I thought it'd be pretty fun if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't like to order or be ordered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, what kind of group are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you could say they're colorless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Colorless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:19.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:24.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unlike the Yellow Napkins and Blue Squares, they don't wear the same color
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}or try to expand their influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Blue Squares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're a color gang that was pretty well known when I was in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't really know much about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but they disbanded after causing some incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you like them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you met the other members?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, not really. You just know their nicknames,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I've met quite a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes at work, or bumping into them on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They were all coincidental though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:58.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, if you think a person is a member, it's usually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well there's no tell-tale sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just ask around like you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most of them will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:17.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ever since I found out that Takiguchi-kun was really part of the Dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I decided to keep it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:25.22,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure he wouldn't like it if other people made a fuss about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.85,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think only those who ask should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:30.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:39.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That concludes the representative meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if the disciplinary staff that Kida-kun's a part of is still meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They should be finishing up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:54.54,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima Mika-san, who was stalking Yagiri Seiji-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.30,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}has been missing since the first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.37,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you learned anything new about Harima-san yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuugamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kida said you should go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:16.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like he's busy debating at the disciplinary staff meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall we go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder what he's debating about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe about uniforms and hair styles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.00,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The princess' commands are absolute, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:44.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, make sure to introduce me to her next time! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:52.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Princess" is the name of a French person I met at Russia Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-She has a piercing on her nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:12:01.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh, so he's gotta be arguing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:08.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've known you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was turning in my entry registration,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the information desk had a list where you could look for your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I saw yours and thought, "That's a pretty cool name,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and then you happened to be in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:25.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I thought it'd be nice to be a class representative with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.32,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:29.62,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't this like what happened with Harima Mika-san and Yagiri Seiji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit, stalkers are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.69,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, if it's a cutie like her it's okay... Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I screw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.62,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}s-she'll stab me to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.95,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-No, maybe she'll be a pyromaniac and burn my place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.99,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, what if she takes my family hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if she has a good personality, being a stalker shouldn't be a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.67,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fact that she's a stalker means she doesn't have a good personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:03.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd just be a nuisance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:08.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't worry. I'm not a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I didn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:13.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:17.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't be. I was just teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.53,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's continue our good relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takeshi, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who? Not me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm talking about you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop acting so innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:08.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks to your friend, I had to buy a new cellphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:12.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... I'm not sure I'm following you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're the pal of the guy who broke my girlfriend's cellphone, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We aren't really friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then who is he? Your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your co-signer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.26,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That reasoning is a little off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You trying to hold a sermon or what, you little asshat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:42.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll teach you about social hierarchy, you little dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:59.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You brought him here because I don't hit girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aw, how considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:06.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd love to make you my girlfriend, but I'm afraid you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:11.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, Ryuugamine Mikado-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was waiting for you near the school gate because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to talk you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:28.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, why is the black bike here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.83,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She must be looking for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, darn! I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good-bye, Sonohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:55.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is way too surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At this rate, they're going to follow me back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.44,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I will hear you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can wait till the black bike's finished her business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, nice to hear from you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-There's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.05,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So she can communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:40.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm looking for my relative's missing daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found her yesterday, but for some reason, she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:57.74,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-She's a terrible liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm afraid I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:07.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How much do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:10.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... You're an urban legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:15.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and you ride a bike without an engine or headlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:30.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... Could you show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}what's behind that helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:37.09,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never imagined I'd have the guts to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.18,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just don't start screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:46.82,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I had the feeling that I'd been waiting for this moment all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:52.92,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still don't know how to describe what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:57.97,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was repeating, "I knew it! I knew it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}deep in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:12.86,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After that, she told me the real reason she was chasing that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.11,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She told me that her name was Selty, and that she was a Dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.38,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About how she came all the way to Japan to look for her missing head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And the girl with a scar around her neck had a head that looked just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.90,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Usually, no one would believe a word of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But for some reason, I believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:38.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I just met her yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I asked her about what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and she said she lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Selty-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can I meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:57.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she's scared of you because you started chasing her so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't we clear up that misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing beats a milkshake with fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:24.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm convinced that this development is a sign that Shocker will become the heroine! {Misaka Mikoto from To Aru}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:28.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! This decides Himegami as the heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:41.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the fuck?!{check timing please}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.53,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He scratched my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chill out, Togusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.92,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That motherfucker is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The light turned red!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll explain the situation to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:12.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want her to see you and think that I'm betraying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's pretty cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:24.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the first time I've heard your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't expect you to be a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.19,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next time you throw a rock at my horse, you'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:52.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, don't you think he's taking too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.85,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Would a cleaning service visit an apartment as run-down as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.65,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:08.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like I said, I just want to know where that girl is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:12.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This strand of hair on the floor is hers, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}P-Please let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've already seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have to dispose of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have to chase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I recognize that van.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe it's from Yagiri Pharmaceuticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:47.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagiri Pharmaceuticals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:47.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:52.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lately their profits have been plummeting, and they're about to be absorbed by a foreign company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.20,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The girl with a scar that went missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.04,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A Dullahan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.21,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People going missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.54,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harima Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagiri Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:05.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Human trafficking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And... the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.77,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:22.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hated an easygoing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be honest, I wasn't really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:32.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please, help me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:35.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted a different life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:39.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've gathered all the pieces. {chess pieces}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:42.39,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bullseye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.92,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.50,0:24:17.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}I hated an easygoing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}I wanted a different life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:25.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}I didn't expect my little wish to affect so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:28.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0015,,{\be1}Next time: Storm and Stress.
